> > +The primary use cases for IOASID are Shared Virtual Address (SVA)
> > and +IO Virtual Address (IOVA). However, the requirements for
> > IOASID  
> 
> IOVA alone isn't a use case, maybe "multiple IOVA spaces per device"?
